{"tid":839104,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"IPHONE仲有加價可能?","createTime":"2018-09-27T16:05:45.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-28T03:44:42.000Z","uid":75790,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"18826cd1c0f84c638ee214683efc7f3d292a6bc3","tid":839104,"uid":75790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T16:05:45.000Z","msg":"係咪件貨冇炒賣市場同佢個供應冇過剩就定價定得啱, ECON好似叫EQ?<br />\n<br />\n始終有人比得起錢買,而IPHONE都冇滯銷, 即是覺得唔值得比錢買嘅人就唔係佢賣嘅TARGET<br />\n<br />\n以前對整個市場嘅需求就價格太低所以咁多人炒同埋要等啦 <br />\n<br />\n依書直說IPHONE未出業績都唔可以話佢貴, 可能仲賺多左錢食埋炒家個TR?<br />\n<br />\n請指教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ,5分ESSAY題<br />\n<br />\n利申:中四補過KELVIN KO"},{"pid":"12b716c47107f7aaea7f2c67740f60a8bb439648","tid":839104,"uid":108090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T16:50:41.000Z","msg":"以往年9-11月黎講<br />\niphone係求過於供，所以市埸會推高個價，之後供應多返就會回落。<br />\n今年，iphone一開波就調高個價，令求過於供嘅情況減輕，自己食埋個層水。所以就冇得炒。"},{"pid":"83e1654396811a60e7d25837635623430afb8400","tid":839104,"uid":108090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T16:53:09.000Z","msg":"但至於定價啱唔啱 要視乎需求彈性。<br />\n依個要睇新iphone嘅銷售量先知，不過Apple應該唔會公布出黎。<br />\n<br />\n如果佢發現調高個價，但最終總收益係少過iphone 6/7/8/x，可能佢又會下調售價。"},{"pid":"e7937c129536f7945a704ee03680f686922030f5","tid":839104,"uid":158977,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T17:05:57.000Z","msg":"彈性<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 加價啲人咪又係狗衝<br />\n所以會再加"},{"pid":"32d0a775e7648b254523aa64b7556be1114b2eff","tid":839104,"uid":25003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e7937c129536f7945a704ee03680f686922030f5","tid":839104,"uid":158977,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T17:05:57.000Z","msg":"彈性<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 加價啲人咪又係狗衝<br />\n所以會再加"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T18:40:33.000Z","msg":"好快20K<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoj